title: Lamucal.com
description: This website offers versatile AI-powered music tools, including a Tabs feature for real-time generation of chords, lyrics, and melodies for any song, an AICover feature that allows you to create song covers using your own voice or celebrity voices, and a Vocal Remover that separates vocals and accompaniment from any song. Whether you're into music creation or song processing, this platform has you covered.
